This tool reads the your F5 BIG-IP LTM configuration file (bigip.conf) and displays it in a simple table format. Works in an offline environment.

How to use it.
1. Click the OPEN button.
2. Select bigip.conf file.
3. Click the START button.

This tool use jQuery from DataTables (https://datatables.net) to format the HTML table.
